    "rationale": "The FEA model ensemble meets pre-specified acceptance criteria for all three QoIs (E/uval < 1.96). Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors are assessed; the majority meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieves level 2 against a required level of 3, which is acknowledged as a limitation but deemed acceptable given the regulatory standardization of ASTM F1717 conditions. The overall credibility evidence is judged sufficient to support a Medium assurance level decision for this Class II device submission.",
